{"tid":1307333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你再唔睇就真係冇得你睇嫁啦！！！","createTime":"2019-07-11T13:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T02:23:42.000Z","uid":256266,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3f418de9aec4212b5a8e82a17124252b471154cb","tid":1307333,"uid":256266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:49:49.000Z","msg":"大家聽左咁多信用體系有幾差 到底有幾on9 其實一早有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實根本所有野都為左咁嚟舖路 唔好仲on99咁扮唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家真係要了解下:<br />\n睇完真係打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n社會信用體系恐佈之處:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/srcGtNTMWvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsrcGtNTMWvs&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=1cc272bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/srcGtNTMWvs</a><br />\n<br />\n《視點31》【黑鏡人生‧淪落失信人】<br />\n「失信人」何以失信、遭遇如何？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sPZ9gSIffjE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsPZ9gSIffjE&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=ee553e8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sPZ9gSIffjE</a><br />\n如何分級？你係貴賓定囚犯？<br />\n滿街偽君子 遍地真小子<br />\n有重病仲要加班 加班加到死 然後係榜樣？<br />\n簡直係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dh4Su3zvRDU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdh4Su3zvRDU&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=4f7c6b60\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dh4Su3zvRDU</a><br />\n《視點31》【新疆監控通道曝光，監控趨勢延伸本港？<br />\n關你咩事 已經殺到埋身啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個港珠澳大橋有咩用？自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XHNQ6fwMf3Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXHNQ6fwMf3Y&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=880747d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XHNQ6fwMf3Y</a><br />\n中國的人臉識別監控系統有多厲害？<br />\n<br />\n你睇完到底有咩感受？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你接唔接受到？<br />\n呢個根本係一個囚犯系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我無嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301237f5c90c3818be5be80fd949a7fbd14a80bb","tid":1307333,"uid":256266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:50:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc1f4564e3674c8aafb00d958e66a0292002ea9","tid":1307333,"uid":256266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43919e781b887c876fe23bc53a5565298967113b","tid":1307333,"uid":256266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:53:37.000Z","msg":"特登整合一下 大家可以一次過睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee7468bc4d1e8e5b89e52b85238bb78e8f53155","tid":1307333,"uid":256266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ee75729592229b417dd7b81746be5f0326f5e0","tid":1307333,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43919e781b887c876fe23bc53a5565298967113b","tid":1307333,"uid":256266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-